[ctns_make id='gen_factoring_the_binomial']

  [ctns_front style='']
The Binomial
  [/ctns_front]  

  [ctns_back style='font-size:76%;width:80%;']
The Binomial is a <strong>factoring problem</strong> that takes the quadratic form $|\begin{gathered}x^2 + Ax = x(x+A), \textrm{ or } \\ x^2 - Ax = x(x-A) \end{gathered}|$ where A is some real number $$A \in \mathbb{R}.$$
  [/ctns_back]  

  [ctns_backspeak]
The binomial is a factoring problem that takes the quadratic form -- exx squared plus ei times x -- which equals exx times the quantity of exx plus ei -- or the quadratic form -- exx squared minus ei times x -- which equals exx times the quantity of exx minus ei -- where is ei -- is some real number.
  [/ctns_backspeak]  

[/ctns_make]
